13:08.237 --> 13:10.193
Molly, hurry up.

13:15.294 --> 13:16.717
Wait.

13:17.778 --> 13:20.589
Never mind, now I'm getting jumpy.

13:22.981 --> 13:24.082
Principal Harod.

13:24.182 --> 13:26.218
What the hell is he doing here
on Christmas Eve?

13:26.318 --> 13:27.973
Keep it down!

13:35.992 --> 13:38.794
- Great.
- I've got flashlights.

13:38.894 --> 13:42.317
- Oh, nice.
- Come on, it's this way.

14:13.122 --> 14:17.714
She better remember us in the will.
It's about time she invited us here.

14:18.593 --> 14:22.196
- She did invite us, right?
- Think of it as a Christmas surprise.

14:22.296 --> 14:25.653
- Taylor!
- 'tis the season. She'll be thrilled.

14:40.043 --> 14:42.500
You see, the thing is...

14:42.678 --> 14:47.382
To be honest, Aunt Etta,
I know you and mom had difficulties

14:47.482 --> 14:52.127
