doesn't even offer me a drink.

15:35.066 --> 15:37.536
I'll help myself, thank you.

15:38.381 --> 15:39.522
Look at this place,

15:39.622 --> 15:43.098
it's like Paul Bunyan and Count Dracula
gayed up and built a dream home.

15:45.286 --> 15:47.309
That is not a toy.

15:48.304 --> 15:51.380
- Oh, hi there, we're the...
- I know who you are.

15:52.590 --> 15:53.990
Okay.

15:54.090 --> 15:57.059
- This is Krampus, right?
- What's a Krampus?

15:57.159 --> 16:00.878
He's like an anti-Santa Claus,
a demon who punishes the naughty.

16:00.978 --> 16:05.118
He whips them, chains them up,
throws them in a sack, stuff like that.

16:05.218 --> 16:10.821
When Krampus knocked, the demon
hunts the wicked from sunset to sunrise.

16:11.321 --> 16:13.322
That's fun.

16:13.422 --> 16:17.024
He comes for little boys
who touch things they shouldn't.

16:17.124 --> 16:18.814
Oops.

16:20.814 --> 16:24.663
- Duncan!
- That was very unwise.

16:24.763 --> 16:28.032
We will pay for it, of course.
Pick it up.

16:28.132 --> 16:31.518
- Gerhart, what have you done?
- I did nothing.

16:31.618 --> 16:35.793
The boy had... an unfortunate accident.

16:37.772 --> 16:41.943
- Take your family and leave now.
- No, let's not be hasty here.

16:42.043 --> 16:45.040
No, my son,
I feel one of my spells coming

16:45.140 --> 16:50.365
and I cannot entertain guests. Goodbye.

17:01.021 --> 17:05.959
Bicycle parts to Sector Five!
Organs sets to arrive!

17:06.059 --> 17:08.048
Video games...

17:08.325 --> 17:11.147
Get out of the way, get out of the way!

17:18.665 --> 17:21.367
Have to take it out again this year.

17:22.435 --> 17:26.159
- Talk to the Mrs., Sparkles.
- Santa, I need your signature.

17:27.304 --> 17:28.640
Thank you.

17:28.740 --> 17:31.008
So what are we up against
this year, Jingles?

17:31.108 --> 17:33.443
Blizzard warning along
the Eastern seaboard.

17:33.543 --> 17:36.145
Never met a blizzard that troubled me.

17:36.245 --> 17:38.566
- It's bad, it's really bad.
- Another signature here.

17:38.666 --> 17:41.313
- I'm worried about the trade winds.
- Trade winds.

17:41.413 --> 17:43.749
- Safety first, Santa.
- Right here on the left.

17:43.849 --> 17:47.839
Lots of kids are depending
on tonight going off without a hitch.

17:50.053 --> 17:51.875
Shiny?

17:53.788 --> 17:56.457
- Take a break, everyone!
- Yay, Mrs. Claus!

17:56.557 --> 17:59.024
Even Christmas magic
needs a little fuel.

17:59.124 --> 18:00.927
- Oh, cookies!
- Smells good.

18:01.027 --> 18:03.316
- Cookies!
- What is this?

18:03.661 --> 18:07.051
- Have a cookie, Shiny.
- No, I...

18:07.663 --> 18:10.799
I don't know. No thank you.

18:10.899 --> 18:13.230
It'll keep your strength up
for the long shift.

18:13.330 --> 18:15.356
I'm not hungry.

18:15.704 --> 18:17.947
Not hungry? They're cookies!

18:18.047 --> 18:21.393
You're being silly, Shiny, you know
how much you love my cookies.

18:22.505 --> 18:26.109
I said I don't want a goddamn cookie!

18:26.209 --> 18:29.199
You reindeer fucking snow whore!

18:30.446 --> 18:32.335
Shiny!

18:51.329 --> 18:53.219
He...

18:53.530 --> 18:55.398
He's dead.

18:55.498 --> 18:57.633
Dead? But elves...

18:57.733 --> 19:02.211
Can't die.
Santa, elves can't die, right?

19:03.736 --> 19:07.126
No. They cannot.

19:12.908 --> 19:15.177
Yeah, he's gonna help
his pop put this up too.

19:15.277 --> 19:18.146
This tree is way better
than the ones at the mall.

19:18.246 --> 19:21.614
- We did it.
- Stop, we can't do this again.

19:21.714 --> 19:23.247
Oh, no way.

19:23.347 --> 19:27.537
They won't even miss it.
They got enough trees around here.

19:33.467 --> 19:37.193
Look at this, babe, this is a perfect tree.
Smells like pine, you love pine.

19:37.293 --> 19:40.295
Yeah, yeah, yeah, I don't think
it's gonna fit up the stairs.

19:40.395 --> 19:43.101
Of course it will,
it'll be fine, trust me.

19:48.033 --> 19:52.058
- Where's Will?
- He was right here with us. Will?

19:53.170 --> 19:54.738
- Will?
- Will!

19:55.738 --> 19:57.307
- Baby!
- Come on, we gotta go!

19:57.407 --> 20:01.051
- This ain't time to play hide and seek now!
- Where are you, babe?

20:03.656 --> 20:06.917
- We gotta go, come on, son!
- Will!

20:13.584 --> 20:16.170
- Come on, boy, stop playing, we gotta go!
- Where are you, baby?

20:16.270 --> 20:18.125
Mom?

20:19.721 --> 20:21.257
- Come on, honey, let's go!
- William, where are you?

20:21.357 --> 20:23.246
Dad!

20:28.128 --> 20:31.096
- William!
- Where are you?

20:31.496 --> 20:32.752
Will!

20:34.731 --> 20:36.832
Where'd he go?

20:36.932 --> 20:39.021
Couldn't have gone far.

20:40.834 --> 20:43.491
- Over here.
- Oh, God.

20:43.903 --> 20:45.859
Will!

20:47.522 --> 20:49.312
Baby?

20:49.774 --> 20:52.112
This way, through here.

20:52.212 --> 20:54.048
Son!

20:54.910 --> 20:56.766
Will!

20:58.045 --> 20:59.935
Will!

21:00.447 --> 21:02.270
Will!

21:03.382 --> 21:05.538
William!

21:08.752 --> 21:10.708
Will!

21:12.054 --> 21:14.277
Oh, God. Oh, God.

21:16.224 --> 21:18.114
Will!

21:26.433 --> 21:28.234
Will?

21:28.334 --> 21:30.557
Come here, buddy!

21:37.575 --> 21:39.231
Scott!

21:42.477 --> 21:45.400
Will. Will!

21:46.691 --> 21:49.803
Come on, baby? Will, are you okay?

21:49.948 --> 21:54.006
What the hell happened?
Why'd you take off like that? Why?

21:54.985 --> 21:58.609
Don't yell at him!
It was your idea to come out here!

22:37.157 --> 22:40.727
Oh, boy, real palace of fun down here.

