weird stories going around

23:06.310 --> 23:09.592
like this 15 year old girl
claimed she was a virgin,

23:09.692 --> 23:13.082
said it was a miracle
like the Virgin Mary, but...

23:13.182 --> 23:14.638
no one believed her.

23:26.961 --> 23:28.929
So what happened to her?

23:29.029 --> 23:32.304
Don't you know, Ben? It was your mom.

23:32.404 --> 23:36.356
No, actually, she died
trying to abort her baby.

23:38.085 --> 23:39.908
Let's go.

24:15.669 --> 24:17.704
This is it.

24:17.804 --> 24:20.239
This is where Connor
and Jenna were killed.

24:20.339 --> 24:22.429
Are you getting this?

24:24.909 --> 24:26.999
You guys hear that?

24:27.427 --> 24:29.145
What?

24:29.245 --> 24:30.468
Stay focused.

24:58.771 --> 25:02.529
- This is where...
- We know. We saw the video.

25:07.167 --> 25:09.246
I wanna make sure
I don't forget anything.

25:09.346 --> 25:11.282
- Yeah? Let's see.
- Yeah.

25:11.382 --> 25:14.134
